cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper heavily relies on image processing techniques using deep convolutional neural networks for feature extraction from images captured by a monocular camera. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics): The paper proposes a new self-driving framework for autonomous vehicles and experimentally validates it on an outdoor track using a 1/5th-scale autonomous vehicle platform. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a human driver control model to achieve more natural driving behavior of self-driving vehicles. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses deep convolutional neural networks for feature extraction from images and relies on machine learning techniques for autonomous vehicle control. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a new framework for autonomous vehicle control and experimentally validates it on a physical platform, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
